Open a command line and go to *this* folder.. (e.g. 'cd /Users/ThinkGareth/Desktop/SinatraTest')


For Heroku deployment type the following lines in the command line. Each line should be executed by pressing return:

	git init
	git add .
	git commit -a -m "All the core bits and bobs.."

Setup Heroku
You'll need a free http://heroku.com account

	sudo gem install heroku
	heroku create my-website-name
	git push heroku master
	heroku open
	
And you should be done!